Medium sized metallic blue or brown flies, 15–19mm . Mid femur with distinct rows of strong dorsal and anterodorsal bristles, a weak basal row of anteroventral black bristles, and strong row of ventral black bristles. Male abdominal tergites metallic blue. Female abdominal tergites dull brown. The male gonostylus is distinctly hooked at apex (
Fig. 24
).
